{"tid":95314,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Netflix 支援離線播放功能，將影片儲存於外置記憶卡中","createTime":"2017-01-26T02:24:09.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-26T02:24:09.000Z","uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ebacf1e6d9536bbd01f6859c2eb009045c46d92e","tid":95314,"uid":1886,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-26T02:24:09.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://www.android-hk.com/wordpress/wp-content/uploads/2017/01/Netflix_4K_UI-640x360.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fwordpress%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2017%2F01%2FNetflix_4K_UI-640x360.jpg&h=32952075&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年 NETFLIX 進軍各地市場，反應大受歡迎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kiss.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。踏入新一年，官方宣佈推出全新的離線播放功能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，更重要的是，大家不用將影片儲存於有限的手機內存空間之中。新功能支援檔案儲存於外置記憶卡之中<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，以後大家就可以隨時隨地享受到優質劇集了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.android-hk.com/news/netflix-offline-play-android-hk-26117/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.android-hk.com%2Fnews%2Fnetflix-offline-play-android-hk-26117%2F&d=9KYqrKSZh%2FQvr90OeAFwMQT5PszEexF2%2B6H4LydsHP4%3D&h=9115d1b4\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.android-hk.com/news/netflix-offline-play-android-hk-26117/</a>"}]}